@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <h2>Your Privacy Matters</h2>

        <p>At WellSpring Tech Academy, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines our commitment to protecting your personal information when you use our website. We encourage you to read this policy to understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your data.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

        <p>We may collect both personally identifiable information and non-personally identifiable information when you interact with our website. The type of information we collect may include:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Contact information (email address, phone number, etc.)</li>
            <li>Demographic information (age, gender, etc.)</li>
            <li>Usage data (such as your browsing habits on our site)</li>
            <li>Other information you provide to us</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

        <p>We use the information we collect for various purposes, including:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Providing and improving our website and services</li>
            <li>Communicating with you, including sending updates, newsletters, and promotional materials</li>
            <li>Responding to your requests or inquiries</li>
            <li>Monitoring and analyzing website usage and trends</li>
            <li>Complying with legal requirements</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Security of Your Information</h2>

        <p>We take the security of your information seriously and implement appropriate measures to protect it. However, please note that no method of data transmission over the internet or electronic storage is entirely secure. While we strive to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>

        <h2>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>

        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We encourage you to periodically review this page for any updates.</p>

        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us <a href="mailto:wellspringtechacademy@gmail.com">here</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
